description: high relief carving going all the way through, mostly on upper half; intricate landscape; figure seated at table with 2 figures standing behind; 4 figures to L of table, 1 blindfolded; 6 figures to PL and below table; separate scene to R with tall standing figure holding baby and 5 smaller figures; detachable base that cylinder does not sit directly upon, 3/4 in. gap
title: Figures in Garden
